### Shadow Effects
- **Style:** {{designSystem.shadows}}
{{#eq designSystem.shadows "none"}}
- Flat design with no shadows
- Clean, minimalist appearance
{{/eq}}
{{#eq designSystem.shadows "sm"}}
- Small, subtle shadows
